languages.text: "Все зеваки немедленно расходятся по своим делам. Беженцы могут отправляться в док Альфа-Ро — я позже с вами поговорю. Слушайтесь, если не хотите проблем".
"All onlookers are to return to their homes immediately. The refugees can go to Dock Alpha-Rho — I will speak to you later. Comply or face the consequences."

languages.text: 「野次馬はただちに家に帰れ。難民たちはアルファ・ローのドックへ進め――後でお前たちの話を聞いてやろう。従わなければ相応の罰を受けてもらう」
languages.original_text: "All onlookers are to return to their homes immediately. The refugees can go to Dock Alpha-Rho — I will speak to you later. Comply or face the consequences."

languages.text: “所有围观民众立刻回家。至于难民，可以去阿尔法罗霍码头呆着，我稍后再过去和你们谈谈。遵守规定，否则后果自负。”
languages.original_text: "All onlookers are to return to their homes immediately. The refugees can go to Dock Alpha-Rho — I will speak to you later. Comply or face the consequences."

languages.text: «Que los curiosos regresen a sus hogares inmediatamente. Los refugiados que vayan al puerto Alfa-Ro. Con usted hablaré más tarde; acate lo que le digo o aténgase a las consecuencias».
languages.original_text: "All onlookers are to return to their homes immediately. The refugees can go to Dock Alpha-Rho — I will speak to you later. Comply or face the consequences."

languages.text: « Que tous les badauds rentrent chez eux. Quant aux réfugiés, rendez-vous sur le quai Alpha-Rho. Je vous y retrouverai plus tard. Obéissez, ou vous subirez les conséquences de vos actions. »
languages.original_text: "All onlookers are to return to their homes immediately. The refugees can go to Dock Alpha-Rho — I will speak to you later. Comply or face the consequences."

languages.text: "Alle Umstehenden kehren sofort nach Hause zurück. Die Flüchtlinge begeben sich zu Dock Alpha-Rho – wir sprechen später. Wer sich weigert, muss die Konsequenzen tragen."

languages.text: "Olayı izleyen herkes hemen evlerine dağılsın. Mülteciler, Alfa-Ro Rıhtımı'na gidebilir. Sizinle orada konuşacağım. Emirlerime uymayanlar sonuçlarına katlanır."

traits.locale_text: "Olayı izleyen herkes derhâl evlerine dönsün. Sığınmacılar Alfa-Rho Rıhtımı'na gidebilir, sizinle daha sonra konuşacağım. Emirlerime uymayanlar sonuçlarına katlanır."
